Hello! I'm brand new to these boards so I wanted to introduce myself. My name is Steve Ewel and I live in Ohio. Many of you know me from other boards but it will be nice to meet new people on here. I have some T206's that I'm getting ready to list on Ebay under my name wabittwax. I would like to sell as many as I can off Ebay ahead of time to avoid excess fees. My email address is [url]wabit2@yahoo.com[/url]. I put the address of the front and back of each card. Thanks!
